<HEAD>
<TITLE>Greenpeace Licensed Products: Message! Checks</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BASE TARGET="_parent">
<BODY BGCOLOR="#FF FF FF" TEXT="#00 00 80" LINK="#00 80 00" VLINK="#80 00 00" 
ALINK="#FF FF 00" basefont=3>
<CENTER><a href="/~usa/index.html"><img src="pix/cam_gear.gif" WIDTH=504 HEIGHT=101 border=0></a></center>
<hr>
<table width=100% border=0>
<tr>
<td valign=top>
<b>"MESSAGE! CHECKS"</b><br>
<font size=-1>Message! Products are checks with a difference. They're 
printed with soy-based inks, they're attractive, they're made from 
recycled paper (20% post-consumer waste), and more than 7% of each 
"Greenpeace Design" check order is returned to an organization you 
believe in. And yes, they're <b>real</b> checks, just like the ones you
get from your bank and they're accepted by all U.S. financial institutions.
<i><b>And they're available EXCLUSIVELY from the 
<a href="http://www.greenmoney.com/message/12green.htm">Message! 
Products website!</a></b></i><p>
</font> 
</td>
<td valign=top>
<a href="http://www.greenmoney.com/message/12green.htm">
<img src="pix/checks.gif" width=288 height=288 hspace=0 ALT="a sample check design" 
border=0></a>
</td>
</tr>
</table>
<hr>
<p>
