<DOCNO>WT04-B26-96</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA083-000586-B036-116</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://greenpeace.org:80/~med/cyprus.html 193.67.176.1 19970103203333 text/html 5943
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Fri, 03 Jan 1997 20:36:11 GMT
