<BR>

<I>Help us in the fight to save our fragile planet!
<BR>
Actions can and <B>do</B> provoke changes!</I>
<P>

Greenpeace does not accept donations from governments, institutions,
political parties and politicians.
<BR>
<B>Greenpeace depends on individuals like
YOU!</B>
<P>
If you want to contribute, fill in this form and send it to Greenpeace
Mediterranean. If you have a <B>Visa</B> credit card, you can fill it
in and send it straight away. But, beware, although the
form won't leave our hands, the channel is unencrypted and the form
may still be unsecure.
<P>
You can also, of course, print out the form, and fax it to us. Or else, mail it to
us at:
<P>

<CENTER>
---------------------------------------(cut here)---------------------------------------
</CENTER>
<P>

<CENTER>
<B>
Greenpeace Mediterranean <BR>
P.O Box 32, <BR>
Paola,
Malta.</B> <P>

Tel: <B>+356 803-463</B>, <BR>
Fax: <B>+356 803-485.</B> <P>
