<H2><TT>Problems?</TT></H2>
Oh dear! If you're desperately trying to send this document over the Internet 
and it just doesn't want to cooperate (computers...), fill in this form, send us a 
normal email message, and include this page in it. If that too doesn't
work, just type in the details yourself and email them to us 
(it's good exercise for your fingers ;)
