                      AC
<B>Israel</B>     17-5-80    21-2-91    3-4-82     28-10-87   14-10-94   -

<B>Lebanon</B>    17-5-80    1994/AC    -          1994/ AC   -          -

<B>Libya</B>      17-5-80    6-6-89/    -          6-6-89/    -          -
                      AP                    AP
<B>Malta</B>      17-5-80    2-3-89     3-4-82     11-1-88    14-10-94   -

<B>Morocco</B>    17-5-80    9-2-87     2-4-83     22-6-90    -          -

<B>Syria</B>      -          1-12-93/   -          11-9-92/   20-9-95    -
                      AC                    AC                               
