<HEAD>

<TITLE>Greenpeace Mediterranean - Incineration (Malta) Petition</TITLE>

<BODY BACKGROUND="pics/tile.gif" BGCOLOR=white Text=black link=blue VLINK=purple ALINK=white>

</HEAD>

<CENTER>
<FONT SIZE=7><TT><B>Stop<BR>
Incineration<BR>
In Malta!</B></TT>
<FONT SIZE=3><BR>
<IMG SRC="pics/redribbn.jpg" ALIGN="absmiddle">
</CENTER>

<P>
<BR>

<CENTER>
---------------------------------------<B>(cut here)</B>---------------------------------------
</CENTER>
<P>
<BR>

The government is seriously considering taking up incineration as part of
its waste management strategy.  
<BR>
Incinerators have been scientifically proven
to be a major source of dioxin, the most toxic man-made chemical. Dioxin is
a major cause of cancer, birth defects and other health killers.
<P>
Instead of opting for the 3 clean alternatives, i.e. reduction, re-use and
recycling of waste, the government is seeking the quickest although least
economical way out.
<P>
If you want to save our islands from this fatal blow, sign this petition as
a form of protest.
<P>
<CENTER>
<PRE>


Name               Address               Telephone               Signature
--------------------------------------------------------------------------



</PRE>
</CENTER>

<CENTER>
---------------------------------------<B>(cut here)</B>---------------------------------------
</CENTER>

<P>
<BR><BR>

<CENTER>
<IMG SRC="pics/exclam.gif" ALT="[!]" ALIGN="bottom">
<BR>
Print the petition,
<BR> fill it in (you, your family, the whole neighbourhood), 
<BR>and mail it (or fax it) at the address below.
<P>
If sending via email, include the text of the petition within the message
and sign with your email address.
<P>
<IMG SRC="pics/exclam.gif" ALT="[!]" ALIGN="top">
</CENTER>
<P>

<CENTER>
<B>
Greenpeace Mediterranean <BR>
P.O Box 32, <BR>
Paola, Malta.</B> <P>

