can never change and delay the implementation of the courts' decisions."
<P> 
2. Scientists appointed by the Aydin Administrative Court spent 1.5 years
working on the expert's report submitted to the court. This report clearly
proves that the power plants concerned cause environmental damage. The 
Ministry of Envirnment claims that recent research on all three plants, using mobile
measuring equipment during one week, showed that these power plants are 
"clean".
