<li><a href="~comms/rw/deport.html">Deportation</a> of GP campaigners</li>
<li> from <a href="~comms/rw/china.html">China</a> in August this year.</li>
<li>Return to the Greenpeace International 
<A HREF="/greenpeace.html">Home page</a></li></ul>
