Chamber</A> <P>
<A HREF="#h_article_40_applicability_of_other_s">  Article 40  Applicability of other sections of this 
Annex</A> <P>
<A HREF="#h_section_5_amendments">  Section 5. AMENDMENTS</A> <P>
