http://greenpeace.org:80/~ozone/hfcs/5test.html 193.67.176.1 19970103181607 text/html 3716
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Fri, 03 Jan 1997 18:18:46 GMT
Server: Apache/1.0.0
