<HEAD>

<TITLE>Greenpeace: An Environmental Imperative</TITLE>


</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF">

<IMG SRC="PosPaper.gif" ALIGN=LEFT ALT="[A Greenpeace International Position Paper" WIDTH="125" HEIGHT="34" BORDER="0">

<IMG SRC="cosmini.gif" ALIGN=RIGHT ALT="[An Environmental Imperative]" WIDTH="300" HEIGHT="34" BORDER="0">
<BR CLEAR=ALL>
<HR>
<P>
<FONT SIZE=+1 FACE="SERIF"><B>
	GREENPEACE ANALYSIS OF HCFC / METHYL BROMIDE PHASE OUT SCENARIOS
</B></FONT>
</P>
<FONT FACE="Helvetica, Arial">
<P>
	Our analysis shows that even if the spirit, as well as the letter,
of the Montreal Protocol is fully adhered to, under the present terms of
the Montreal Protocol, the ozone layer will not recover until around
2040. At the same time, the Greenpeace calculations show that an
emergency phase out of ozone depleting substances, including early phase
out of HCFCs and methyl bromide, could accelerate recovery of the ozone
layer by nearly fifteen years (to 2026) and this would reduce ozone
depletion by nearly 40%.
</P>

</FONT>
<HR>
<P ALIGN=CENTER>
<A HREF="1intro.html"><IMG HSPACE=3 SRC="../gfx/gpdotbk.gif" ALT="[back]" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="28" BORDER="0">
</A>
<A HREF="index.html"><IMG SRC="../gfx/gpdotup.gif" ALT="[return to index]" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="28" BORDER="0">
</A>
<A HREF="3consume.html"><IMG  HSPACE=3  SRC="../gfx/gpdotfd.gif" ALT="[next]" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="28" BORDER="0">
</A></P>
</BODY>
</HTML>
