<DOCNO>WT04-B26-165</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA082-000568-B039-184</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://greenpeace.org:80/~ozone/costa/6prod.html 193.67.176.1 19970103180354 text/html 1979
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
