<DOCNO>WT04-B26-166</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA082-000568-B039-192</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://greenpeace.org:80/~ozone/costa/7other.html 193.67.176.1 19970103180401 text/html 3413
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Fri, 03 Jan 1997 18:06:42 GMT
