<DOCNO>WT04-B26-167</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA082-000568-B039-200</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://greenpeace.org:80/~ozone/costa/8ods.html 193.67.176.1 19970103180409 text/html 3692
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
