<P>The Statement of Assets and Liabilities and the Statement of 

Income and Expenditure of Greenpeace International for the year 

ended December 31, 1993 and December 31, 1994, included on this 

page, are derived from the financial statements of:


<P>Stichting Greenpeace Council, Amsterdam, The Netherlands;

<BR>Stichting Marine Services, Amsterdam, The Netherlands;

<BR>Greenpeace Communications Ltd, London, United Kingdom;

<BR>Greenpeace International Inc., Washington DC;

<BR>and entities holding compensation received from the French 

government in 1988.



<P>Unqualified audit opinions were expressed, on various dates, on 

the 1993 and 1994 financial statements of these entities.



<P>Amsterdam, June 1995

<BR>KPMG Accountants NV
