<DOC>
<DOCNO>WT04-B26-202</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA082-000568-B039-118</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://greenpeace.org:80/~ozone/unep_ods/9frozen.html 193.67.176.1 19970103180236 text/html 2070
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
