</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#ffffff">
<IMG SRC= "../icons/gpclogo.gif" ALT="Greenpeace Logo"><BR>
<H3><B>HIDDEN VICTIMS OF THE DROUGHT </B></H3><P>

Small non-farm businesses in Australia's  drought- afflicted
regions  are being forced to close down as a result of the
economic downturn in these areas. A recent survey suggests that
70 percent of businesses in these regions have experienced an
average revenue drop of 28 percent, 25 percent of them had to cut
staff, and as many as a third have gone out of business.
("Drought devastates 'hidden victims'", The Australian, 16
November 1994).<P>

