<TITLE>WARMING "NOT A MYTH"</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#ffffff">
<IMG SRC= "../icons/gpclogo.gif" ALT="Greenpeace Logo"><BR>
<H3><B>WARMING "NOT A MYTH" </B></H3><P>

The head of the Hadley Centre for Climate Prediction and Research
at  the UK Meteorological Office, Dr David Carson, refutes a
newspaper article headlined "Met Office says global warming is
just a myth". Dr Carson states:  "there is clear observational
evidence of ... global-scale warming in this century" and
"anthropogenic emissions of greenhouse gases have been, and will
increasingly be, a significant contributing factor". He goes on
to say that while sulfate aerosols have probably slowed warming
to some extent, their influence was transitory, and that in time,
"the enhanced greenhouse effect will dominate". (Letter to the
editor, Sunday Times [London], 18 September 1994).<P>

GREENPEACE Climate Impacts Database<P>

